<body class="bg-amber-50">
<div class="min-h-screen">
<!-- ヘッダー -->
<header class="bg-white shadow-sm">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 sm:py-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<%= image_tag "/kakehashi-dm-logo.svg", class: "w-8 h-8 sm:w-12 sm:h-12", alt: "ロゴ" %>
<h1 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-amber-700">かけはし糖尿病・甲状腺クリニック</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>

<!-- メインコンテンツ -->
<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 sm:p-8">
<!-- タイトル -->
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-700 text-center mb-6">診療科を選択</h2>
<p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-8">翌日〜4週後までの予約が可能です</p>

<!-- 診療科選択ボタン -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto mb-8">
<a href="/appointments/new?department=internal_medicine" 
   class="block px-6 py-4 text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-400 to-amber-500 hover:from-amber-500 hover:to-amber-600 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105">
<span class="text-lg">内科</span>
<div class="text-sm mt-1">（木曜・日曜は休診）</div>
</a>

<a href="/appointments/new?department=kampo" 
   class="block px-6 py-4 text-center bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-500 font-bold rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all duration-200 cursor-not-allowed opacity-60" 
   onclick="return false;">
<span class="text-lg">漢方</span>
<div class="text-sm mt-1 text-gray-400">（準備中）</div>
</a>
</div>

<!-- 注意事項 -->
<div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-amber-200">
<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">＊ 漢方のWEB予約は現在休止中です</p>
<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">＊ 発熱や風邪症状がある方、および<span class="font-semibold">コロナ検査を希望</span>される方は直接お電話ください</p>
</div>
</div>
</main>

</div>
</body>
